                     <interp inst="t18260216-113-person788" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took her into custody, and asked her about the things, but she gave no answer.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg my mother's pardon.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 15.</p>
